{"tid":1301631,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對不起！我決定原諒林鄭！","createTime":"2019-07-09T16:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:24:48.000Z","uid":255509,"like":563,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"8d85455ad6c53883359c5ca4ca37261d80c03ded","tid":1301631,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i6T9J1Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi6T9J1Z.png&h=b55a4641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n依條柒婆林奠死都唔肯收返<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撤回</span></span>兩字<br />\n係咁做人肉錄音機<br />\n各位巴絲唔係原諒佢呀？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">熱門一個關於7.14嘅post都無！！！</span></span><br />\n大家唔可以就咁比佢沉！<br />\n大家唔以比今次遊行<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「壽終正寢」</span></span><br />\n要話比林奠知唔回應5大訴求香港人係唔會罷休<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家依幾個星期已經好體力透支<br />\n但係香港需要我地一齊抗爭！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">被捕嘅義士需要我地！<br />\n比我地更加辛苦嘅前線需要我地！<br />\n和理非一定要發揮我地嘅用處，</span></span><br />\n香港需要大家！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">7.14沙田要人啊！<br />\n沙田要人啊！<br />\n沙田要人啊！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/10/001936_a52aafb6da3627b602914ca9d7f8d05d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F001936_a52aafb6da3627b602914ca9d7f8d05d.png&h=b12d24ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/10/001938_52f93e394fe7f826f899a6c2ba379bd6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F001938_52f93e394fe7f826f899a6c2ba379bd6.png&h=cce552dc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEoeaQf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEoeaQf.png&h=4b70d53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">齊上齊落！<br />\n不撤不退！<br />\n遍地開花！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">沙田遊行Tg group <br />\n而家100個人都未夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家麻煩入一入谷同share<br />\n求求大家幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位<br />\n沙田見！"},{"pid":"89b8462578bb6d64c72bcf03c3b2acc7b028c08f","tid":1301631,"uid":200758,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AiR3F8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAiR3F8V.jpg&h=f4a2740b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EuDmAd2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEuDmAd2.jpg&h=28455d55&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b424cf1b7d479215b3f4ca9a17827ed516b34104","tid":1301631,"uid":255509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"644aa3289eb530aa000620d7254cd14ed32a148f","tid":1301631,"uid":232671,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:45:08.000Z","msg":"唔好意思, 借個位<br />\n香港人權和民主法案係今次成敗關鍵, 請大家務必勾結外國勢力, 以造成外憂內患局面<br />\n<img src=\"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/news/624/cpsprodpb/FF21/production/_104431356_hi050738606.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F624%2Fcpsprodpb%2FFF21%2Fproduction%2F_104431356_hi050738606.jpg&h=7ce03555&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7beb4db5a5728b7e8244468a9ccf666ab707db30","tid":1301631,"uid":255509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"推呀"}